Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是難得的新社員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得太普通會被認為很無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我會這樣認為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有律這樣想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快畫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我自己畫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長她們怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來了  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  叫她小律就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平澤學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我唯就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  紬紬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒錯  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想看著可愛的學妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛好乾…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能眨眼竟然這麼痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個社團真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪是扮姐姐啊  是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？  完全不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過了嗎  要拍得像全家福一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全家福？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快點坐下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這就是中野梓的入社紀念了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家笑一個～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入社紀念嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  高三今天不是已經沒課了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有很重要的東西要送過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個之前玩過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的婆婆給了我八朔橘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拿吃的東西來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業照？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我說今天樣本會送到  大家就說要到學校來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像無論如何都想看一下的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看了  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打開了  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼額頭在發光啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我拍得很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼用這張照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我選的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐們  比起那個  那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再拿吃的東西玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…唯拍得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得很有小唯的感覺  很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有我的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說像小孩子一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太直接了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  和和  這個還只是樣本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  把相機拿來  我要重拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的  一定要用正規的相機拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去拿正規的相機來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要照顧每個人的意見的話  就沒完沒了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  這可不是普通的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是畢業照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會一直流傳下去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過個100年也會被保留著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆的同學的劉海好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…會變成那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎  讓人家留下了深刻的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐是有點任性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和也真堅決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  現在有件傷腦筋的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是佐和子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是要她今天檢查好後  明天就送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是說不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為感冒請假了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶  整人成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小佐和竟然會感冒  真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓小佐和檢查也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  如果小佐和說這照片要換的話就會換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為此而檢查的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片應該換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換張更可愛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:06:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以拜託你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  因為是我們的畢業照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平時要有幹勁啊  唯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上也能猜出她在打什麼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人生活的老師的房間～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也有個激動不已的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能看到老師的私生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  梓就努力上好下午的課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後  音樂教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒什麼  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒別的路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  乖乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也別和它搞得這麼熱乎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是老師的家離得不是很遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼近的話就能睡到8點多了  真是幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像的要普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為小佐和的家一定會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘等著你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼家啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊  澪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…就這樣去會不會給她添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是感冒嗎  一個人一定很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝的東西也買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總會有隱私的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱私？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男…男朋友在  之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連紬也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  403室的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有點緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要按咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  這裡是405！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好道歉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人開門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒人在家啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中要有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像在警戒著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在鄰居都不在  出來也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼高興？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要按了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行公務！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家不缺東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏他已經暴露了  束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師已經被完全包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您母親在哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷偷摸摸在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在隱藏什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是垃圾啊  垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很麻煩  就想要不要就這身打扮去扔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別撒謊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為這樣就能矇混…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擾民了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打聽了我的住所？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是特地來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是小小的感冒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有件非常重要的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情？  什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～也不算什麼重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那明天再說也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  今天打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…還沒定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定了就告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼樣都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4  5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面也挺普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都沒有男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒勁兒～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不住你們了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒想得那麼嚴重  我們也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咯  那麼開始調查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:45.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們擔心了  其實我一直睡到中午才起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因此燒也退了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要打開…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現小佐和過去的衣服！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦～好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看溫度又要上去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  小佐和的畢業相冊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和好年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你照片蠻好看的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說來您看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你說的重要事情  就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和正在發愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就拿來老師這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  稍微等下  我現在檢查一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請  請問～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我覺得有張照片也許換一下可能比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  哪張哪張？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…  是這個叫做平澤唯同學的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看額頭這裡有點不太對頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎？挺可愛的嘛  很像你的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看唯的肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什什什什什什麼啊？！這照片！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這裡確實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼時候拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我記得是修學旅行之前一段時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼久的事情…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這張照片就換一下好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…啥事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛想起什麼事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？沒…沒想到啥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你幹的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…這個…其實…這事呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在是對不住你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太對不住你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就不換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那老師檢查剩下照片的時候我們來做飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那順便也幫忙打掃和洗衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也想做飯～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也比較傾向下廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！那我們猜拳決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦  猜拳決定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那倒也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:47.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是石頭  石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次  一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬給我贏啊！紬紬給我贏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了！勝利的剪刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咯  讓你們見識下我的真本事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你不用那麼幹勁滿滿啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  先準備一合大米…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一合是多少公斤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一合相當於中文裡一升的1/10）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天還能去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師嗎  不好意思突然打電話給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐她們還在您那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呢  你要不要也過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正好在做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個  這麼說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們暫時還會留在那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐她們還在老師家裡  應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得倒也不用這麼偷偷摸摸的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我會擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓她們看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  不努力點的話我會把光腳的照片放到畢業相冊上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  杯子稍微往右點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  別動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後會變安靜了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  味道不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現黑色內衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你在孤零零生病  還專門帶大家來看你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  一起吃了飯再走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還要回學校一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡擠九個人也有點小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來你們已經畢業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今年三月  我們考上同一所大學了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輕音社明年怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我說又準備廢社了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少成員？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在幫我們圓場吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.35,0:18:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過看她一副自信十足的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有希望加入的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會以為我們明年會繼續留在輕音社啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是你  怎麼可能會搞錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是注定留級了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是她沒說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梓喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…唯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:29.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續一會吧  學姐她們還沒回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小佐和老師是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都這時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新歡演奏會上還要多演奏一首吧  不努力點怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙練習也蠻有趣  我完全沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙她們練習啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑…跑啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  學姐  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新歡演奏會  好好加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  這次我慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯你跳得早了點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下張就不改了  我要回辦公室了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一～二」就跳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  你也練習一下比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一次都沒失敗過  別擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:21:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳慢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去海邊  而是要去海外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音部打算去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.13,0:23:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想去海外
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where very delicious cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  姐姐你們居然要去海外…我稍微有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where my hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要去海外嗎
